&lt;h3 id="42-现代狼人黑夜传说暮光"&gt;4.2 现代狼人（黑夜传说/暮光）&lt;a class="anchor" href="#42-%e7%8e%b0%e4%bb%a3%e7%8b%bc%e4%ba%ba%e9%bb%91%e5%a4%9c%e4%bc%a0%e8%af%b4%e6%9a%ae%e5%85%89"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
